{"tid":1391994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8月5日捐一日糧！！","createTime":"2019-07-31T15:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T02:48:18.000Z","uid":95138,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"78ec743e26cbf1057b1c05ee2c6cd03503082fcb","tid":1391994,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:10:12.000Z","msg":"雖然都知道大家買防具/捐物資洗左好多錢<br />\n但係今次至今已經有172位義士被捕<br />\n佢地好需要我地嘅支援<br />\n<br />\n所以希望大家罷工之餘，同時發起捐一日糧行動<br />\n支持所有被捕義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b966253c2b954f4622dc6d557ea810f98b007be","tid":1391994,"uid":68822,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:13:36.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DErY1NGl2p_M&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFvUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=1359402c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwGX_Vgq-1G0&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFvUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=4374f0e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0</a><br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！時代革命！<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong! <br />\nThe Revolution Of Our Times! </span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>五大訴求</strong></span></span></ins><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4. 追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>Hongkongers 5 Demands:</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n1. Full Withdrawal of the Extradition Bill<br />\n2. Retraction of the Characterisation of the Protestas a Riot<br />\n3. Release all Arrested Protesters<br />\n4. Accountability for Police and Yuen Long White Shirts Brutality<br />\n5. Implement Dual Universal Suffrage<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Rcba2Hh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcba2Hh.png&h=a61a5d44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/fm6yf2o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffm6yf2o.jpg&h=67e4b0d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時間無多，政府拖字訣，想我地自亂陣腳，行動規模必須升級</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49429d1d05ec37cf1b8b937e61dfc5874651adfb","tid":1391994,"uid":95138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:14:24.000Z","msg":"612人道支援基金 612 Humanitarian Relief Fund<br />\n612人道支援基金工作及捐款方法<br />\n<br />\n基金的主要工作是為反送中運動中受傷、被捕或有關人士，提供人道支援，包括醫療、心理/精神，法律及其他有關援助。<br />\n<br />\n612人道支援基金捐款方法<br />\n1. 銀行轉帳或經「轉數快 / FPS」轉帳至由「真普選聯盟有限公司」設立之基金專用戶口，匯豐銀行：652-255761-001，FPS ID 3261476。<br />\n也可以經匯豐櫃位或自動櫃員機入支票或現金，支票詳情見（2）。<br />\n請留意基金戶口每日經自動櫃員機存入現金上限為港幣10萬元，如當日總額已超出上限將無法存入。<br />\n<br />\n2. 以支票抬頭「真普選聯盟有限公司」或「Alliance for True Democracy Limited」<br />\n可直接經銀行櫃位或ATM存入銀行，或<br />\n寄往「九龍旺角山東街51號中僑商業大廈7樓 612人道支援基金收」，信件及支票背面請註明「612人道支援基金」。<br />\n<br />\n3. Paypal 戶口：612fund@atd.hk<br />\n<br />\n4. 海外捐款 / International Wire Transfer<br />\nBank Name : The Hongkong &amp; Shanghai Banking Corporation Limited<br />\nBranch Address : 1 Queen's Road Central Hong Kong<br />\nSwift Code : HSBCHKHHHKH<br />\nAccount Name : Alliance for True Democracy Limited<br />\nAccount Number : 652-255761-001<br />\nCompany Address : 7/F, Chung Kiu Commercial Building, 51 Shantung Street, Mongkok, Kowloon<br />\n<br />\n備注：<br />\n1. 基金不接受任何有條件捐款，如基金收到港幣100,000元以上具名或不具名的單筆捐款，將會對外公佈。<br />\n2. 如捐款者要求收據，請保留入數紀錄並透過Facebook專頁或電郵與我們聯絡，惟收據並不能作扣稅之用。<br />\n3. 基金戶口分行編號 (Branch code) 為：652，即帳號頭3個數字。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/notes/612人道支援基金-612-humanitarian-relief-fund/612人道支援基金工作及捐款方法/390380584995445/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fnotes%2F612%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%93%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91-612-humanitarian-relief-fund%2F612%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%93%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%8F%8A%E6%8D%90%E6%AC%BE%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%2F390380584995445%2F&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFvUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=ac8580ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/notes/612人道支援基金-612-humanitarian-relief-fund/612人道支援基金工作及捐款方法/390380584995445/</a>"},{"pid":"ee7b5c5d13432c64b168e956b24b680b50e2294e","tid":1391994,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:16:22.000Z","msg":"【大搜捕●不斷更新】6.12至今 至少172人被捕  - <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190731&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59799844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190731%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59799844&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFvUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=5402ddf8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190731%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59799844&h=a124e329\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190731&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59799844</a>"},{"pid":"6dc426208ff0a1aa956acc37fdcab90c48dfbf86","tid":1391994,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:20:25.000Z","msg":"仲有好多受傷義士需要支援"},{"pid":"affb5cc353668e82dc66cd356569d370e4ca06e2","tid":1391994,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:22:57.000Z","msg":"仿效無國界醫生 捐一日糧 tag三個朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f07cd959d3fa59ea4ae0baf96b8a1cf18577e39b","tid":1391994,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:24:40.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"fe5893ee29962ede04ed7f4b63088229d8114106","tid":1391994,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:25:24.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"d895d48fd97bc997ef7482f27cbddaa7b7804a77","tid":1391994,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:29:06.000Z","msg":"轉數快FPS ID 3261476"},{"pid":"79c12d864cd1caab61a41ba0dfdd1e2f1a3b8693","tid":1391994,"uid":262022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:32:48.000Z","msg":"我要罷工"},{"pid":"c107bd6274c0d28eec82890551a39e15d72c4da8","tid":1391994,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:32:50.000Z","msg":"之前捐左 5/8都可以再捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda7623dc606d6762cf3e815543b408b3e293f3f","tid":1391994,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79c12d864cd1caab61a41ba0dfdd1e2f1a3b8693","tid":1391994,"uid":262022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:32:48.000Z","msg":"我要罷工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:36:11.000Z","msg":"我要捐一日糧"},{"pid":"8fc86bf9488daee9bc5a97460bd9a4bed02c69cb","tid":1391994,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:39:13.000Z","msg":"我地要所有抗爭者安心出黎抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc3fad2e787141901d28a165e31746b70cefd056","tid":1391994,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:42:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97164e48348c12acdc7b8877aed04bf743426199","tid":1391994,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:46:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7250f565b70ce586acb87b4076d8eb20f72b2fda","tid":1391994,"uid":46534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:46:46.000Z","msg":"我哋由612開始爭取成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n不過，我哋從來冇討論過委員會由咩人去組成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多人分析琴日中共為成立獨立調查委員會開綠燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋係時候開始討論當中嘅細節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n試過有法官判示威者以胸部襲警後，相信大家都明白香港有好多紅底法官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以獨立調查委員會一定唔可以只係有本地法官組成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要嘅獨立調查委員會係<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>由國際專家、聯合國，甚至海牙軍事法庭嘅人組成</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拒絕港共自己人查自己人<br />\n<br />\n要由國際專家調查事件</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8bd42f86b89d5ea12b48a4db42c618aebb8b160","tid":1391994,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:49:00.000Z","msg":"入票又得 ATM入錢又得"},{"pid":"343821a0f44b109f24a8409cfeacb413a2e1b257","tid":1391994,"uid":4979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:49:43.000Z","msg":"係咪捐612基金?"},{"pid":"31e26f7fc2729a605598e4fdb81ae42f63717170","tid":1391994,"uid":6594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:50:35.000Z","msg":